  "subject": "Add policy deployment status to Pdp structure",
  "commit_message": "Add policy deployment status to Pdp structure\n\nModified the Pdp (and JpaPdp) structures, adding lists of policies\nawaiting deployment and undeployment.  To support this, added toConcept\nand fromConcept methods to ToscaPolicyIdentifier, and also made\nPfUtils.mapList() more generic (i.e., can now take one type and return\nanother type).\nAlso added bumpXxx() methods to PolicyStatus to facilitate counting the\ndeployment status of policies.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-2648\nChange-Id: I769d44d155bbc4e19e063ddb70faf145ce6966aa\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\n",
